thread.title: Two Ohio police officers shot to death, suspect held

title: Two Ohio police officers shot to death, suspect held
text:
Two Ohio police officers shot to death, suspect held Saturday, February 10, 2018 - 02:31 
Two Ohio police officers were shot to death on Saturday when they responded to a call and a suspect was wounded and is in custody, a spokeswoman for the city of Westerville said. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
